text: More facts have been revealed since Ben Stiller and Christine Taylor shockingly announced they would be calling it quits after 17 years of marriage. Most fans were stunned because the couple, who have even appeared onscreen together in recent years, seemed to have everything together, especially for a Hollywood couple. According to however, that is far from reality.
title: The Secret Life! Ben Stiller & Christine Taylor Had Arguments Over ANOTHER Woman
